      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this beauty in person to believe it. \ud83d\ude97\u2728 I\u2019ve taken such incredible care of this car that it honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. There isn't a single blemish on it, and the interior is still looking absolutely flawless\u2014it\u2019s been my total pride and joy! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been truly babied and is ready for a new home, this is definitely the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come by and fall in love with it yourself!",
