    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for the discerning collector is a pristine 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in Carbon Black Metallic. This example is powered by the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six engine, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. The mechanical integrity is superlative: the dual-VANOS system has been fully bulletproofed, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with precision-welded plates. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry remains true, with all bushings and dampers exhibiting factory-spec dampening. This vehicle retains its original VIN-matched body panels and showcases a flawless interior with Nappa leather. Accompanied by a comprehensive service dossier, this M3 represents the pinnacle of analog driving dynamics.",
